{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a responsive Shopify “Video Product Spotlight Duo” section with 3D interactive product cards and quick add buttons.
    
    Purpose:
    
    Showcase exactly two featured products using product videos as the main visual. The section should feel premium, playful, modern, and suitable for Tabasquishy® collectible sensory toys.
    
    Layout:
    
    - Display only 2 products.
    
    - Section heading and subtitle at the top.
    
    - Desktop layout:
    
      - Two large product spotlight cards side by side.
    
      - Each card should feature a video as the main media.
    
      - Cards should feel like premium 3D interactive product tiles.
    
    - Mobile layout:
    
      - Stack the two product cards vertically.
    
      - Keep videos responsive and tap-friendly.
    
      - Disable complex 3D tilt on mobile.
    
    - Match the Shopify theme page width and side margins.
    
    - Use max-width and margin auto.
    
    - Mobile side padding should be around 16px–20px.
    
    - No horizontal page overflow.
    
    Product card requirements:
    
    - Product video as the main visual.
    
    - Product image fallback if video is not available.
    
    - Product title.
    
    - Price.
    
    - Compare-at price if available.
    
    - Sale badge if compare-at price exists.
    
    - Short product description or custom text.
    
    - Quick Add / Add to Cart button.
    
    - If the product is unavailable, show a disabled “Sold Out” button.
    
    - Use the first available variant by default.
    
    - Rounded corners with a soft, larger border radius.
    
    - Soft shadow or subtle border.
    
    - Clean spacing.
    
    - Product media should stay inside the card and never overflow.
    
    Video requirements:
    
    - Support Shopify-hosted video or uploaded video setting for each product card.
    
    - Video should autoplay muted, loop, and playsinline.
    
    - Add a poster image / fallback image setting for each video.
    
    - Video must crop neatly inside the card using object-fit: cover.
    
    - Add optional video controls setting in schema.
    
    - On mobile, keep video lightweight and responsive.
    
    - Do not autoplay sound.
    
    - Make sure the section still looks good if video fails to load.
    
    3D interaction:
    
    - On desktop only, add subtle 3D tilt effect based on mouse movement.
    
    - The product card should gently rotate in 3D when the mouse moves over it.
    
    - The video/image should slightly zoom or lift on hover.
    
    - Card shadow should become slightly stronger on hover.
    
    - Add a soft glow or depth layer behind the card if possible.
    
    - Add smooth transition when the mouse leaves.
    
    - Disable 3D tilt on mobile and tablets if needed.
    
    - Respect prefers-reduced-motion and disable or reduce animation when needed.
    
    - Keep animations smooth, subtle, and performance-friendly.
    
    - Avoid overly flashy animation.
    
    Quick Add functionality:
    
    - Each product card must include an Add to Cart button.
    
    - The button should add the first available variant of the selected product to the cart.
    
    - Use Shopify AJAX cart API if possible.
    
    - After adding, temporarily change button text to “Added!”
    
    - If adding fails, show “Try Again”.
    
    - Do not redirect the customer unless the theme requires it.
    
    - JavaScript should be scoped to this section and should not affect other theme scripts.
    
    Design style:
    
    - Premium, cute, playful, modern.
    
    - Suitable for a collectible sensory toy brand.
    
    - Strong visual focus on video.
    
    - Use soft rounded cards, clean typography, and comfortable spacing.
    
    - Avoid clutter.
    
    - The two products should feel like a curated spotlight, not a normal product grid.
    
    Schema settings:
    
    - Section heading.
    
    - Section subtitle.
    
    - Background color.
    
    - Background image.
    
    - Background image overlay opacity.
    
    - Text color.
    
    - Card background color.
    
    - Card border radius.
    
    - Card shadow intensity.
    
    - Button color.
    
    - Button text color.
    
    - Button hover color.
    
    - Show/hide sale badge.
    
    - Show/hide product description.
    
    - Enable/disable 3D tilt.
    
    - Enable/disable video controls.
    
    - Section top padding.
    
    - Section bottom padding.
    
    - Maximum content width.
    
    - Card gap.
    
    - Product 1 picker.
    
    - Product 1 custom video.
    
    - Product 1 poster/fallback image.
    
    - Product 1 custom description.
    
    - Product 2 picker.
    
    - Product 2 custom video.
    
    - Product 2 poster/fallback image.
    
    - Product 2 custom description.
    
    Accessibility and performance:
    
    - Use semantic HTML.
    
    - Use accessible buttons.
    
    - Add aria-labels where needed.
    
    - Respect prefers-reduced-motion.
    
    - Lazy load videos when possible.
    
    - Keep JavaScript lightweight.
    
    - Prevent layout shift.
    
    - Prevent horizontal overflow on all screen sizes.
    
    Please generate a complete Shopify Liquid section file with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and schema. Make the two product cards feel like floating 3D video posters:
    
    - Add a soft layered shadow behind each card.
    
    - Add a subtle perspective transform on desktop hover.
    
    - Add a small floating label on each video, such as “New Drop” or “Best Pick”.
    
    - Add a glassmorphism-style info panel at the bottom of each video card.
    
    - Keep the Add to Cart button inside the info panel.
    
    - On mobile, keep the info panel simple and readable., 减少3D效果, 头图显示有问题，没有展示1:1的头图, 我要商品头图区域展示完整的1:1的头图，你的地步的商品信息部分把头图遮挡了
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-video-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-top: {{ block.settings.padding_top }}px;
    padding-bottom: {{ block.settings.padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }}::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: url('{{ block.settings.background_image | image_url: width: 2000 }}');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    opacity: {{ block.settings.bg_overlay_opacity | divided_by: 100.0 }};
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: {{ block.settings.max_width }}px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    font-family: {{ block.settings.heading_font.family }}, {{ block.settings.heading_font.fallback_families }};
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_bg_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  {% if block.settings.shadow_intensity > 0 %}
    .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      box-shadow: 
        0 {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity | times: 2 }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity | times: 4 }}px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
        0 {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity | times: 2 }}px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }
  {% endif %}

  @media (hover: hover) and (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    {% if block.settings.enable_3d_tilt %}
      .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 
          0 {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity | times: 3 }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity | times: 6 }}px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12),
          0 {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity | times: 1.5 }}px {{ block.settings.shadow_intensity | times: 3 }}px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }

      .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover::before {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-media-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-video-{{ ai_gen_id }},
  .ai-video-spotlight-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  @media (hover: hover) and (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-video-spotlight-video-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-video-spotlight-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      transform: scale(1.03);
    }
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-label-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    left: 16px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2c2d2e;
    z-index: 3;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  {% if block.settings.show_sale_badge %}
    .ai-video-spotlight-sale-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      position: absolute;
      top: 16px;
      right: 16px;
      background: #c62a32;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      z-index: 3;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-video-spotlight-info-panel-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_bg_color }};
    flex-grow: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1c1d;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-price-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2c2d2e;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #9fa3a7;
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  {% if block.settings.show_description %}
    .ai-video-spotlight-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #2c2d2e;
      opacity: 0.8;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      display: -webkit-box;
      -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
      -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
      overflow: hidden;
      flex-grow: 1;
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-video-spotlight-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_color }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text_color }};
    border: none;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius | divided_by: 2 }}px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_color }};
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled {
    background-color: #9fa3a7;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    transform: none;
  }

  .ai-video-spotlight-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}:disabled:hover {
    background-color: #9fa3a7;
    transform: none;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-video-spotlight-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 0 16px;
    }

    .ai-video-spotlight-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .ai-video-spotlight-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .ai-video-spotlight-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .ai-video-spotlight-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      transform: none !important;
    }

    .ai-video-spotlight-info-panel-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .ai-video-spotlight-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .ai-video-spotlight-price-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-video-spotlight-video-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-video-spotlight-image-{{ ai_gen_id }},
    .ai-video-spotlight-button-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      transition: none !important;
    }

    .ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      transform: none !important;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<ai-video-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }} class="ai-video-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-video-spotlight-container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.heading != blank or block.settings.subtitle != blank %}
      <div class="ai-video-spotlight-header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
        {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
          <h2 class="ai-video-spotlight-heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        {% if block.settings.subtitle != blank %}
          <p class="ai-video-spotlight-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subtitle }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-video-spotlight-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% for i in (1..2) %}
        {% liquid
          assign product_key = 'product_' | append: i
          assign video_key = 'product_' | append: i | append: '_video'
          assign poster_key = 'product_' | append: i | append: '_poster'
          assign description_key = 'product_' | append: i | append: '_description'
          assign label_key = 'product_' | append: i | append: '_label'

          assign product = block.settings[product_key]
          assign custom_video = block.settings[video_key]
          assign poster_image = block.settings[poster_key]
          assign custom_description = block.settings[description_key]
          assign custom_label = block.settings[label_key]
        %}

        <div class="ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}" data-card-index="{{ i }}">
          <div class="ai-video-spotlight-media-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if custom_video != blank %}
              <video
                class="ai-video-spotlight-video-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                autoplay
                muted
                loop
                playsinline
                {% if poster_image != blank %}
                  poster="{{ poster_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                {% elsif product.featured_image %}
                  poster="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                {% endif %}
                {% unless block.settings.show_video_controls %}
                  disablepictureinpicture
                {% endunless %}
                {% if block.settings.show_video_controls %}
                  controls
                {% endif %}
                aria-label="Product video for {{ product.title | escape }}"
              >
                <source src="{{ custom_video }}" type="video/mp4">
              </video>
            {% elsif product.featured_media.media_type == 'video' %}
              {{ product.featured_media | video_tag: 
                autoplay: true, 
                loop: true, 
                muted: true,
                controls: block.settings.show_video_controls,
                class: 'ai-video-spotlight-video-' | append: ai_gen_id
              }}
            {% elsif product.featured_image %}
              <img
                src="{{ product.featured_image | image_url: width: 800 }}"
                alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="800"
                height="800"
                class="ai-video-spotlight-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
            {% else %}
              <div class="ai-video-spotlight-image-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if custom_label != blank %}
              <div class="ai-video-spotlight-label-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ custom_label }}</div>
            {% endif %}

            {% if block.settings.show_sale_badge and product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
              <div class="ai-video-spotlight-sale-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                SAVE {{ product.compare_at_price | minus: product.price | times: 100 | divided_by: product.compare_at_price }}%
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          <div class="ai-video-spotlight-info-panel-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if product != blank %}
              <h3 class="ai-video-spotlight-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.title }}</h3>

              <div class="ai-video-spotlight-price-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <span class="ai-video-spotlight-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.price | money }}</span>
                {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
                  <span class="ai-video-spotlight-compare-price-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
                {% endif %}
              </div>

              {% if block.settings.show_description %}
                <div class="ai-video-spotlight-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {% if custom_description != blank %}
                    {{ custom_description }}
                  {% elsif product.description != blank %}
                    {{ product.description | strip_html | truncate: 100 }}
                  {% endif %}
                </div>
              {% endif %}

              <button
                class="ai-video-spotlight-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                data-product-id="{{ product.id }}"
                data-variant-id="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}"
                {% unless product.available %}disabled{% endunless %}
                aria-label="Add {{ product.title | escape }} to cart"
              >
                {% if product.available %}
                  Add to Cart
                {% else %}
                  Sold Out
                {% endif %}
              </button>
            {% else %}
              <h3 class="ai-video-spotlight-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Select a product</h3>
              <p class="ai-video-spotlight-description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Choose a product to showcase in this spotlight card.</p>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</ai-video-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }}>

<script>
  (function() {
    class AiVideoSpotlight{{ ai_gen_id }} extends HTMLElement {
      constructor() {
        super();
        this.cards = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-video-spotlight-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.buttons = this.querySelectorAll('.ai-video-spotlight-button-{{ ai_gen_id }}');
        this.enable3DTilt = {{ block.settings.enable_3d_tilt | json }};
      }

      connectedCallback() {
        this.setupQuickAdd();
        if (this.enable3DTilt && window.matchMedia('(hover: hover) and (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference)').matches) {
          this.setup3DTilt();
        }
      }

      setupQuickAdd() {
        this.buttons.forEach((button) => {
          button.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
            e.preventDefault();
            if (button.disabled) return;

            const variantId = button.dataset.variantId;
            const originalText = button.textContent;

            button.textContent = 'Adding...';
            button.disabled = true;

            fetch('/cart/add.js', {
              method: 'POST',
              headers: {
                'Content-Type': 'application/json',
              },
              body: JSON.stringify({
                id: variantId,
                quantity: 1
              })
            })
            .then(response => response.json())
            .then(data => {
              button.textContent = 'Added!';
              
              if (window.theme && window.theme.cart) {
                window.theme.cart.refresh();
              }
              
              document.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('cart:refresh'));

              setTimeout(() => {
                button.textContent = originalText;
                button.disabled = false;
              }, 2000);
            })
            .catch(error => {
              console.error('Error adding to cart:', error);
              button.textContent = 'Try Again';
              setTimeout(() => {
                button.textContent = originalText;
                button.disabled = false;
              }, 2000);
            });
          });
        });
      }

      setup3DTilt() {
        this.cards.forEach((card) => {
          card.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
            const rect = card.getBoundingClientRect();
            const x = e.clientX - rect.left;
            const y = e.clientY - rect.top;
            
            const centerX = rect.width / 2;
            const centerY = rect.height / 2;
            
            const rotateX = (y - centerY) / 40;
            const rotateY = (centerX - x) / 40;
            
            card.style.transform = `perspective(1000px) rotateX(${rotateX}deg) rotateY(${rotateY}deg) translateY(-4px)`;
          });

          card.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
            card.style.transform = '';
          });
        });
      }
    }

    customElements.define('ai-video-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }}', AiVideoSpotlight{{ ai_gen_id }});
  })();
</script>

